{
  "stem": "24466.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm talking about-- it's mixed up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm talking about the time when I was working for the Russian army, Red Army, and before for [NON-ENGLISH] in the Omega, straightaway at the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got the letters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father asked me to help him, to help them, to help them-- the daughter of Dr-- of the director, of Jack, that what I mentioned to you already in the-- previously.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you had no-- are you saying you had no contact--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I haven't got--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--no contact whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I have to mention here things what are not-- it's hard for me to talk about this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But still, I have to tell it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When Vilna start judenrein, become judenrein, and the ghetto was to the concentration, to the extermination camps-- sent away, a day before it happens, that that Rabbi Lvowicz with the wife-- because they didn't have already the children-- they were taken away-- two children-- a little boy, Nomi, and the other one, I forget the name.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of the commandants from our bock took that Rabbi Lvowicz with the wife and send them to the ghetto, for sending him away to the examination camps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The name of that commandant from the police, from the police there, was Krawczynskae.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-R-A-W-C-Z-Y-N-S-K-A-E-- Lolek.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His first name was Lolek.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came from my work, from the tanneries back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I find out what happens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I ask him what happens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, you want to have your rabbi back here?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The test will cost-- will cost you $300.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told him, Lolek, I accept this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bring me back the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You will get the $300.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was Lolek with the Jewish police?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He commanded the-- the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They are different.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
